 ][ region of beauty and delight ][ .  There, Margaret, the sun is forever ][  ][ visible, its broad disk just skirting the hori
zon and diffusing a ][  ][ perpetual ][  splendour.  There--for with your leave, my sister, I will put ][  ][ some trust in prec
eding navigators--there snow and frost a ][ re banished; ][  ][ and, sailing over a calm sea, we may be wafted to a land surpass
