ut just  ][ at that time I inherited the fortune of my cousin, and my ][  ][ thoughts were turned into the channel of their earl
ier bent. ][ ][   ][ Six years have passed since I resolved on my present undertaking.  I ][  ][ can, even now, remember the hou
